To troubleshoot this issue:

1. Check if there are any running background processes related to Office or other potentially problematic software.
2. Run a full system scan using reputable antivirus/antimalware software.

If you're concerned about the performance impact of these duplicate files, you can delete them after confirming they are not needed by any running processes. However, always be cautious when deleting system files to avoid potential stability issues.
